==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outride
<hw>Out*ride"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To surpass in
speed of riding; to ride beyond or faster than.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outride</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Outride
<hw>Out"ride`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A riding out; an
excursion.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A place for riding out.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outrider</ent>⟦br⟧
